	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a 26 mage also and find the experience at the gnoll spires in S. Karana awesome.&nbsp;&nbsp;Go to Nexus, get KEI, go to S. Karana and camp the south spire.  You will get the highest level gnolls popping there (still some yellow and red every now and then) as well as some roamers.  Bind there since you will want to run to Nexus to get KEI and pop right back as quickly as possible.  From what I've heard you can camp there until low 30's....you can also go inside PAW but be careful, it can get hairy in there.  Hope this helps. <br><br>Oops, almost forgot...you also get an experience bonus for fighting there....I get about 1/2 to 3/4 blue bub per kill there :)  (Solo only unless you get bored)<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Apr 21 16:35:13 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Angg (21 monk - Tarew Marr)<br>Elorian (51 druid - Tarew marr)<br><br>Hand to hand combat is the only true test of a man's ability to survive.</td></tr>
