	   <tr><td colspan=2>In answer to your question, brell's fishing pole is an effect on a planes of power item. For some reason it's been listed on the spell.dat file as a mage spell for ages. To my knowledge, if a scroll for it exists, it's never been found. I wouldn't sweat it. Also, take everything on casters realm with a grain of salt. They're notorious for apocryphal or totally innacurate information that they are extremely reluctant to correct. For instance the mage summoned earring is still listed as an aggro reducer there. It reduces mana. Not aggro. Been listed that way since luclin came out. My appoligies if they finally corrected that.<br><br>As to mages being ruined past 60.... Not if you do it right. Seen a 65 mage solo phinny before. heh.<br><br><br><br>Faelawen Starfyre, the Mad Mage of Povar, Leader of Defiant Heroes, 58th season, arch nemesis of the evil squirrel empire.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
