	   <tr><td colspan=2>Also if you cannipet be sure to buy something with the appropriate level of Summoning Efficiency I, II III...etc. One that I use is <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1899." target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1899.</a> It is good til lvl 60. How it works is that you use less mana when summoning those pets that you canni. Also using the lower level pets grants you more mana than if you used the higher level one then reclaimed it. (At least that was the last word I got/witnessed).<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Apr 21 08:17:20 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Boka Slyfox <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=658921" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=658921</a><br>38 Rogue ~ Tunare Server<br>/ooc 38 Rogue looking for a Guild. I dont do raids, dont do groups...I like to steal and ninja loot PST</td></tr>
