	   <tr><td colspan=2>Thanks for all the info...VERY helpful.&nbsp;&nbsp;One last thing on Cannipetting, is there a particular item that you recommend to use to reduce the amount of ingredients used for your pets.  I know that the Summoning Efficiency will work real well with reducing the mana I use in casting but don't want to spend a ton of cash on malchite and such trying to regain mana (I might as well go to Nexus and get KEI, it'd be cheaper).  I know there's quite a few items out there but any reccomendations would be great.<br><br>Thanks again.<br>&nbsp;<br>Angg (21 monk - Tarew Marr)<br>Elorian (51 druid - Tarew marr)<br><br>Hand to hand combat is the only true test of a man's ability to survive.</td></tr>
