	   <tr><td colspan=2>Easy tip for newbie mages:<br><br>It IS possible to take more than one mob at a time. I am lvl 53 and can still take two Dark Blue cons at once.<br><br>The strat?<br><br>Using earth pet, wait till he roots one, then back off until he pulls back, then he roots 2nd, the split now. Burn on the one he's fighting... Root doesn't usually last long so you need to back off again etc, but it saves ALOT of pet hps. <br><br>Lansiere Enriele &lt;Exegesis&gt;<br>53rd Mage of Tunare<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
